                <h3>Step 2: Identify Object References</h3>
                <p>Look for patterns like:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>IDs:</strong> /api/posts/12345, /api/users/67890</li>
                    <li><strong>UUIDs:</strong> /api/comments/a1b2c3d4-e5f6-...</li>
